Nemesis Enforcer/Scatterblaster/Vehement/Teufel:



Nemesis Enforcer flew backwards in result from a missile, courtesy of 
Vehement.  The psychotic robot slammed to the ground with an "Oohf."

"Die traitor!" Scatterblaster yelled, tackling 'Zardus' in mid, both of them 
crashing to the ground hard.

"Get off!" Teufel, who was still using his holographic technology to look 
like Zardus, yelled, sending a clawed hand to tear at Scatterblaster's face.
